text:
You can no longer install iOS 13.1.2 and iOS 13.1.3
07 Nov 2019, 08:25 by Artyom Bausov
Apple stopped signing iOS 13.1.2 and iOS 13.1.3. This means that you can no longer install them. Roll back, respectively, too.
Now the current version of the operating system is iOS 13.2.
